msgstr "可以混合配置区间和单个值。例如 10-30 填 30%，31-50 填 10%。"

msgid "The start of the range. In fixed amount mode, enter the discount amount directly."
msgstr "区间起点。固定金额模式下直接填写优惠金额。"

msgid "The value of a single prize. In fixed amount mode, enter the discount amount directly, for example 20."
